5	b) wanted / was	"Want" es roca. No necesita Past Perfect. "Already closed" = pasado simple.	La roca no se moviÃ³ dos veces.
6	b) recognized / had known	"Recognized" = acciÃ³n puntual (Past Simple). "For years" ANTES = Past Perfect.	Reconocimiento (flash) + conocimiento previo (archivo).
7	c) read / will have left	"By the time" + presente simple. AcciÃ³n COMPLETADA antes = Future Perfect.	LÃ­nea de meta. Llegas antes de que lean.
8	c) will have been / will be working	"By Friday" = Future Perfect. "All week" = duraciÃ³n en futuro = Future Continuous.	Meta + proceso.
